title: Fida Dog Rope Toys for Large Dogs, 92cm Indestructible Dog Toys for Tug of War, 100% Natural Cotton Chew Toy for Boredom, Pulling, Teeth Cleaning
features: SAFETY COMES FIRST - We always design all our products with safety in mind. This dog rope toy is made from natural cotton.

DESIGNED FOR LARGE DOGS - 92cm, 750g, 5 knots of 9cm width, 3 strands of rope tightly interwoven. These numbers mean that the dog rope toy is of heavy duty quality and can withstand greater pulling and tugging forces from the dog.

TUG OF WAR - This product is like a shorter version of a tug of war rope, strong and durable, suitable for both indoor and outdoor play. Perfect for tug of war games between us and our dogs to strengthen the bond. Even better if you have two dogs, they'll be fighting over this rope every day.

TEETH CLEANING - It's in a dog's nature to chew. While your dog is chewing on this tough dog rope toy, he is also cleaning his teeth and reducing tartar. This dog toy will keep your dog away from your furniture.

RESPONSIBLE CUSTOMER SERVICE - Fida takes responsibility for every product. We offer a 30 day mo.ney back guaran.tee and a 1 year wa.rranty(replacement) so you can shop with confidence. If you have any problems please contact us, we are here for you 24/7!
